        "body": "<p>Discover should act as the main storytelling destination for the brand. It replaces a fragmented collection of About pages with one clear editorial journey, while still giving each major subject enough room to feel important.</p><p>The page introduces Seppeltsfield at a high level, then leads users into deeper dedicated templates. The links in this mockup already anticipate the Shopify routes we may need to build.</p>",
